what_worked: Applied prefetch_fact_join, multi_dimension_prefetch, single_pass_aggregation: Applied aggressive multi-CTE prefetch by creating staged CTEs for filtered dimensions (item and date_dim) before joining with the fact table. This reduces the catalog_sales scan early by pushing down selective filters. The conditional aggregations remain consolidated in a single scan.
why_it_worked: Pre-joining filtered dimensions with fact table before aggregation reduces join input; Pre-filtering multiple dimension tables in parallel reduces join fan-out; Consolidating repeated scans into CASE aggregates reduces I/O from N scans to 1
